{"tid":603402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國 0:6 威爾斯】威爾斯女足﹕巴利如跟小童踢球","createTime":"2018-03-23T17:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T06:56:50.000Z","uid":60281,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9d3afd9a7dd0e2714f4294eb3164d99942a43b","tid":603402,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180323/s00006/3984d799f2a767ae4285976c88757a4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180323%2Fs00006%2F3984d799f2a767ae4285976c88757a4e.jpg&h=53ebf774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚中國盃揭幕戰被敵鋒加里夫巴利三度破門，終以0：6慘負客軍「紅龍」威爾斯，賽後內地傳媒以「慘案」來形容這次恥負，內地球迷亦群情洶湧，對主教練納比及一眾國腳口誅筆伐，惟震撼力或不及為威爾斯女足歷來最佳射手的凱倫華特（Helen Ward）一句話：「巴利似與一班兒童踢球。」<br />\n<br />\n31歲的凱倫華特在英國廣播公司（BBC）形容中威之戰的印象如下：「威爾斯男足自在得像在操場上踢波。巴利似與一班兒童踢球。」曾代表英格蘭U23女足出賽1次的凱倫華特，於2008年轉為威爾斯女足效力，司職前鋒的她迄今上陣70次入42球。<br />\n<br />\n至於吞下威爾斯6蛋的國足是輸掉隊史第2場最大敗仗，賽後受到內地球迷炮轟，指他們「打出了世界杯（盃）巴西對德國的水平（巴西2014年世盃1：7負德國）」，亦有「先見之明」的指出「看到3比0就關電視了」。此役雖被列為「慘案」，卻有球迷反其道稱「這不是慘案，這是中國足球的正常發揮」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大聖撚狗精華<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/kivd4WGBIuWlw7Hitn/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fkivd4WGBIuWlw7Hitn%2Fgiphy.gif&h=b1fc6397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/X8VF9hwCiH3cNktEHZ/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FX8VF9hwCiH3cNktEHZ%2Fgiphy.gif&h=68e4846e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/35zNQTxipzlhwBLxbl/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F35zNQTxipzlhwBLxbl%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c30a4d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3gQLe8P0qlG5rjFzYX/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3gQLe8P0qlG5rjFzYX%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a76b066b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92b4c15461b14105715f51731e379870f7a8793c","tid":603402,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:05:39.000Z","msg":"巴利你有大聖依個名都係我地中国人既小說作出黎架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識唔識飲水思源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"398495082ede778903f6041fbdc7b34b46d2e645","tid":603402,"uid":158755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"瘋狂包越位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4880ef60f9ca3ddea0f2e4b47d63b02f699ec1e8","tid":603402,"uid":39632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"有球VOKES係禁區跑返轉頭拎波果球 條後防仲差過雪糕筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11f81fe83b81c6b8fa0c849e8ad69bcf3ca5063","tid":603402,"uid":18276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:14:23.000Z","msg":"0 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e1953d676a586ead02d0e0deb16631254757e6","tid":603402,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4880ef60f9ca3ddea0f2e4b47d63b02f699ec1e8","tid":603402,"uid":39632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T17:10:32.000Z","msg":"有球VOKES係禁區跑返轉頭拎波果球 條後防仲差過雪糕筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:50:34.000Z","msg":"弱過2015打香港果隊"},{"pid":"ca3d345e41de8a6a3929f258e4d5869ed7bd2738","tid":603402,"uid":42152,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"第四張gif個中場喺度散步睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56